@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome false

title FCTF Login Flow

actor User
participant "Contestant Portal" as Portal
participant "Challenge Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Auth Service" as Auth

User -> Portal: Open login page
Portal -> Auth: Submit username/password
Auth --> Portal: JWT token
Portal -> Gateway: Request challenge list (JWT)
Gateway --> Portal: Challenge data
Portal --> User: Show dashboard

@enduml
